Vb6.0 basic coding methods

1.ByVal is added when used as a parameter in sub or function.
  The parameter will not just be a ref but will be a real newly instanced value
2.Form is widely used（frm），which is like

Public Form Form1
    xxxx
    Sub initializeComponent
    End Sub
End Form

or some thing。

Basically，it is like class module，but always having interface and .frm，not cls file.

3.Class module extended：

 ClassA （Yes，like this）
     field sentences xxx
     method sentences xxx
 End ClassA
 
 exported as cls
 
 4.common module extended：
  ModuleA
      fueldxxxx （common module has the same life time with project.So as well as the data here）
      methodXXXX
  End ModuleA
  
  5.We widely use VB6.0 to make desktop form developments！
